"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"個撚個港豬都high 大撚咗，聽到淋奠嘅有字幕，有埋稿，錄起咗咁講「徹回」就打撚哂飛機，噴精噴到虛撚哂脫<br />\n<br />\n我屌撚哂你地老豆老母呀！條撚樣係講「<strong>動議徹回</strong>」呀！<br />\n<br />\n要先等到垃圾會復會；仲要排期；仲可以突登揾啲垃圾議案排前啲，打埋尖插埋隊；經過建制派班冚家富貴投嘅反對票；經過二讀；<br />\n<br />\n班建制撚屌仲可以學當年三子咁玩拉布<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月嘅斷手，斬人，強姦，爆頭，盲眼，催淚彈，布袋彈，海綿彈，動真槍，死人<br />\n都仲未同你計呀！<br />\n<br />\n仲要五大訴求一樣都冇呀！<br />\n徹回-&gt;動議徹回<br />\n徹暴動定性-&gt;冇！<br />\n獨立調查委員會-&gt;監警會<br />\n釋放被捕人士-&gt;冇！<br />\n雙普選-&gt;冇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同中共講妥協？<br />\n而家要搞革命先脫離到中共管治呀！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我呢個魔警都諗撚到啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">千祈千祈千祈要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好習慣！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n香港警察，知法犯法<br />\n社會垃圾，吞槍自殺<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"76256277ec78f1452835220d647d0844ac449923","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15071ef8dc3c67326ebe74d282b20c16038990d","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"勇武快D轉方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d72fe27095abd7100b01c05f5b465ab343315cb","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c8145214db2110f356a98afdddc2345b5df058","tid":1541541,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"特別認同呢幾日會不斷有前高官賢達商人等出黎發聲明讚揚特首知所進退呀能屈能伸呀深曉大義之類<br />\n和理非我都認為做得唔夠<br />\n真係需要全方位文宣加抵制藍屍商戶<br />\n對勇武既建議亦都讚同<br />\n圍狗屋其實真係同送頭冇分別...地下化小隊化係必需<br />\n同埋真係會係漫漫長路"},{"pid":"ae1072db47e83c59b29ee283e02b378086449692","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"一齊入黎傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6b19f2f1a0f71c2510ed32d56f460ba18783a7","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c8145214db2110f356a98afdddc2345b5df058","tid":1541541,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"特別認同呢幾日會不斷有前高官賢達商人等出黎發聲明讚揚特首知所進退呀能屈能伸呀深曉大義之類<br />\n和理非我都認為做得唔夠<br />\n真係需要全方位文宣加抵制藍屍商戶<br />\n對勇武既建議亦都讚同<br />\n圍狗屋其實真係同送頭冇分別...地下化小隊化係必需<br />\n同埋真係會係漫漫長路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"已經唔會返到六月九號前既香港"},{"pid":"8e7475540610a1aedb4effa5683bf2f140581f58","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e2ee2cf024e58a5b711c5b79aa80d61b358be0","tid":1541541,"uid":299642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係時候轉方法"},{"pid":"1c663f8c4fcf4b936be3a6daa0b6547347c2a282","tid":1541541,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite